content: These guys were worth the money
Needs a larger selection; would even pay for more. But it's not worth having an entire icon in the app drawer for this. Find a way to hide the app icon in the app drawer.

love this when it actually appears in my Gboard sticker menu

It doesn't work from Gboard itself. Have to go into separate app to send. Doesn't look as good as regular Google stickers because background is white versus transparent. Hopefully the kinks get worked out and I can send them directly from the keyboard. Thanks.
gg

It's okay. For $1.99 I expected much more than what is offered. I cannot even access the app in Android Messages, I have find the app and then select the sticker, then attach it, then send it. Not user friendly.
This needs more stickers. Spider Man ASAP.
I love it but could add more people and wish they'd add it to my keyboard for easy access
These are soooo cute!!! I love them!!

Awesome

Cute. But very low resolution though.
I like the stickers, but they won't show up on GBoard, which is what I wanted them for. I also can't use them on Twitter, only as a direct message, which is weird.
The stickers are nice but are too big. In the app they're nice and small but when I use them as texts they're gigantic

MARVELous fun! Please add some missing MCU characters like Spidey, Hawkeye, Falcon, Vision, Nick Fury and Agent 13. Would be great to get the Defenders as well.  Hope we also get a Comics variants set in the future. Excelsior!
Fun stickers! Hoping there are more Marvel sticker pack apps coming to Google Play. (I would absolutely love a Kawaii Marvel pack, or ten!!)
Awesome stickers, but would love to see a few more characters added for the price.

Good stickers. Would be nice if there was an option to hide the app icon from the launcher though. I'll be using these stickers exclusively through Gboard so I don't need to ever open the app. Right now it's unnecessary clutter.
I wish there was way more variety.
